skf.config

Interface ConfigurationInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Configuration

    public interface ConfigurationInterface
    The root interface in the Configuration hierarchy. A configuration is a set of parameters related to the SEE event, which are used by the SKF framework to set up a SEE Federate on the specific RTI infrastructure.
